. Issues for <May 9, 1843-July 19, 1861> called also <new ser., v. 2, no. 71-new ser., v. 19, no. 1020>. Daily eds.: Daily advertiser and farmer, Sept. 8, 1856-186, and: Evening farmer, 186 -18, and: Bridgeport evening farmer, 18 -1917, and: Bridgeport times and evening farmer, 1918-192. New series vol. CXVII, no. 5107 (title from masthead) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed September 23, 2015). New series vol. CXXVIII, no. 5729 (August 13, 1920) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed September 23, 2015)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:03.421Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2015218855/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fairfield", "bridgeport", "danbury", "connecticut", "fairfield county", "united states"], "number": ["192107503", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "online resource", "2381-0114", "2015218855", "2015218854", "2015218853"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Issues for <Aug. 12, 1864-Feb. 1865> published as: Bridgeport Republican farmer", "Issue for <Aug. 24, 1866> published as: Weekly Republican farmer", "Issue for <May 21, 1897> published as: Weekly farmer"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "republican farmer (bridgeport, conn.) 1803-192? [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 66.91796, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD AN1 .A15", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "fairfield county (conn.)", "bridgeport", "fairfield", "agricultural newspapers", "bridgeport (conn.)", "danbury (conn.)", "connecticut", "danbury", "fairfield county", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:52:06.072Z", "title": "Republican farmer", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2015218855/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://infoweb.newsbank.com/?db=EANX&s_browseRef=decades/14DE99CA2A23A1A6/all.xml", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82015536/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn82015536", "http://infoweb.newsbank.com/?db=EANX&s_browseRef=decades/10F19F342FFB91C0/all.xml"], "batch": ["ct_haddam_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1803", "description": ["Weekly Vol. 1, no. 1 (Nov. 16, 1803)- Published in Bridgeport, Conn., <May 23, 1810-> Publisher: Stiles Nichols & Son <July 12, 1815-> Issues for <May 9, 1843-July 19, 1861> called also <new ser., v. 2, no. 71-new ser., v. 19, no. 1020>. Available on microfilm from Recordak, Readex Microprint Corp., and the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Daily eds.: Daily advertiser and farmer, Sept. 8, 1856-186, and: Evening farmer, 186 -18, and: Bridgeport evening farmer, 18 -1917, and: Bridgeport times and evening farmer, 1918-192."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:01.070Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "ndnp/newspapers", "main-catalog-split-15", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82015536/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [41.179195, -73.189476], "location": ["fairfield", "bridgeport", "danbury", "connecticut", "fairfield county", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-73.189476, 41.179195], "number": ["new york pub libr res libr", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82015536/1909-04-02/ed-1/", "microfilm master", "new york state - vx6", "131", "online resource", "2381-0106", "sn84022472", "new york univ", "connecticut state libr", "1", "microfilm service copy", "sn82014093", "2020-12-07t13:02:06.271773", "library of congress", "boston pub libr", "connecticut hist soc", "2025-06-27t06:57:54", "new haven colony hist soc libr", "new york state libr", "new york hist soc, newsp proj", "fairfield hist soc libr", "derby pub libr", "northwestern univ", "n